== Monetary == * ''daler'' – From 1534, Swedish [[thaler]]. From 1873, replaced by the ''[[Swedish krona|krona]]''. * ''riksdaler'' – From 1624, {{frac|1|1|2}} ''daler'', from 1681 2 ''daler'', from 1715 3 ''daler'', from 1776 6 ''daler'' * ''skilling'' – From 1776, {{frac|1|48}} ''riksdaler'' * ''mark'' – From 1534, {{frac|1/3}} ''daler''. From 1604, 1/4 ''daler''. * ''öre'' – From 1534, 1/8 ''mark''. Subsequently replaced by the ''skilling'', but from 1855 reintroduced as 1/100 ''riksdaler''.
